    "These codes were subsequently organized into broader themes by grouping related concepts.",
    "For instance, themes like \"ethical dilemmas, \" \"pedagogical impacts, \" and \"cultural considerations\" were identified as central to the research objectives.The identified themes underwent iterative review to ensure consistency and alignment with the data.",
    "Overlapping themes, such as \"bias detection\" and \"bias mitigation, \" were consolidated under the broader theme of \"bias and fairness. \"",
    "Each theme was then clearly defined and scoped to capture its unique aspects.",
    "For example, the theme \"cultural considerations\" was defined as addressing the potential for LLMs to perpetuate dominant cultural norms while marginalizing diverse perspectives.Finally, the themes were synthesized into actionable insights, which are presented in the Results (Sect. 4) and Discussion (Sect."
